{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/selector-max-universal/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/selector-max-specificity/","description":"selector-max-type 限制一个选择器中类型选择器的数量 此规则在计算类型选择器的数量之前先解析选择器嵌套。选择器列表中的每个选择器都将单独计算。 :not() 伪类的内容也是单独计算的。此规则将其参数视为一个独立的选择器，结果不计入整个选择器的总数。 选项…","title":""},"body":"<h1 id=\"selector-max-type\"><a href=\"#selector-max-type\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>selector-max-type</h1>\n<p>限制一个选择器中类型选择器的数量</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">    <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {}\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/** ↑\n * 这种选择器 */</span></code></pre>\n<p>此规则在计算类型选择器的数量之前先解析选择器嵌套。<a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/selectors4/#selector-list\">选择器列表</a>中的每个选择器都将单独计算。</p>\n<p><code>:not()</code> 伪类的内容也是单独计算的。此规则将其参数视为一个独立的选择器，结果不计入整个选择器的总数。</p>\n<h2 id=\"选项\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>选项</h2>\n<p><code>int</code>：允许的最大类型选择器数量。</p>\n<p>例如，使用 <code>2</code>：</p>\n<p>以下模式被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">span</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  &#x26; span {}\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  &#x26; > a {}\n}</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">div</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">div</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 选择器列表中的每个选择器都将单独计算 */</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">div</span>,\n<span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">span</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* `span` 在 `:not()` 里面，所以它是单独计算的 */</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:not(span)</span> {}</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<h2 id=\"可选的辅助选项\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%89%E7%9A%84%E8%BE%85%E5%8A%A9%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>可选的辅助选项</h2>\n<h3 id=\"ignore-child-compounded-descendant-next-sibling\"><a href=\"#ignore-child-compounded-descendant-next-sibling\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>ignore: [\"child\", \"compounded\", \"descendant\", \"next-sibling\"]</code></h3>\n<h4 id=\"child\"><a href=\"#child\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>\"child\"</code></h4>\n<p>不计算子类型选择器。</p>\n<p>例如，使用 <code>2</code>：</p>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">span</span> > <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-id\">#bar</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">span</span> > <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {}</code></pre>\n<h4 id=\"compounded\"><a href=\"#compounded\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>\"compounded\"</code></h4>\n<p>不计算复合类型选择器————即与其他选择器链接的类型选择器。</p>\n<p>例如，使用 <code>2</code>：</p>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">span</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">span</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-id\">#bar</span> {}</code></pre>\n<h4 id=\"descendant\"><a href=\"#descendant\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>\"descendant\"</code></h4>\n<p>不计算后代类型选择器。</p>\n<p>例如，使用 <code>2</code>：</p>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">span</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-id\">#bar</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">span</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {}</code></pre>\n<h4 id=\"next-sibling\"><a href=\"#next-sibling\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>\"next-sibling\"</code></h4>\n<p>不计算紧邻兄弟类型选择器。</p>\n<p>例如，使用 <code>2</code>：</p>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> + <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">span</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-id\">#bar</span> + <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">div</span> + <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">span</span> + <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> + <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">span</span> {}</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"ignoretypes-regex-regex-string\"><a href=\"#ignoretypes-regex-regex-string\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>ignoreTypes: [\"/regex/\", /regex/, \"string\"]</code></h3>\n<p>给定：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-js\">[<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"/^my-/\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"custom\"</span>]</code></pre>\n<p>例如，使用 <code>2</code>。</p>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">custom</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">my-type</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">my-other-type</span> {}</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/selector-max-type.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/selector-max-type/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/selector-max-type/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/selector-max-type/index.html.58f6df3f81a124ccec3e8c6cef06b54a.json"}